## ⚙️ **.gitignore**

Here’s the C++-specific `.gitignore` (includes macOS, VS Code, and build artifacts):

```gitignore
# macOS system files
.DS_Store

# Compiled object files
*.o

# Compiled dynamic libraries
*.so
*.dll
*.dylib

# Compiled static libraries
*.a
*.lib

# Executable files
*.exe
*.out
*.app

# Debug and build files
*.dSYM/
*.obj
*.log
*.tmp
build/
cmake-build-*/

# VS Code or editor settings
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# JetBrains CLion / IntelliJ
.idea/

# Code::Blocks project files
*.cbp
